**HumanGuard** is a unique CLI tool designed to protect you from **Social Engineering** and improve your **Daily Digital Safety**. 

Most security tools focus on firewalls; **HumanGuard** focuses on the "Human Firewall".

## Features

- ğŸ•µï¸ **Social Engineering Check**: Analyze suspicious messages for phishing indicators.
- ğŸ”— **URL Safety**: Quick check for malicious URL patterns.
- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Daily Safety Tip**: Get a fresh tip every day to stay safe online.
- ğŸ”‘ **Password Strength**: Local-only analysis of password complexity.
- ğŸ“š **Learning Modules**: Interactive scenarios to learn how hackers manipulate people.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
# Get a daily safety tip
hg tip

# Analyze a suspicious message
hg check "Hey, I'm from your bank. Click here to reset your password."

# Check a URL
hg url "https://google-login-secure-update.com"
```
